{"tid":2195030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果踢爆： 鄭若驊老公潘樂陶做主席既安樂工程項目8月兩次洩漏劇毒無通報","createTime":"2020-09-09T02:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T11:42:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"85a265666f347c9c09045194543d842bf7afd185","tid":2195030,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》獲悉，元朗新圍污水廠8月兩次洩漏劇毒硫化氫，第一次硫化氫濃度是1ppm（百萬分之一），第二次濃度11.6ppm，達到危險水平。香港大學化學系博士鄺士山（K Kwong）指，硫化氫濃度超過10ppm可導致人眼痛和嘔吐，若超過100至150ppm，1至4小時可致死。項目承建商安樂工程涉密冚洩毒事故，無通報事件予消防處和環保署。而安樂工程主席是潘樂陶，其妻子是律政司司長鄭若驊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PBKP7GFHS5HM5NLHXKRRJIS6YI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0UJWV2MBedSYCNTaZcJFk12I5nXn5dzELmOMbT_6BqqojXJuyJ7nL5TWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPBKP7GFHS5HM5NLHXKRRJIS6YI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0UJWV2MBedSYCNTaZcJFk12I5nXn5dzELmOMbT_6BqqojXJuyJ7nL5TWo&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=18096b16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPBKP7GFHS5HM5NLHXKRRJIS6YI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0UJWV2MBedSYCNTaZcJFk12I5nXn5dzELmOMbT_6BqqojXJuyJ7nL5TWo&h=24363f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PBKP7GFHS5HM5NLHXKRRJIS6YI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0UJWV2MBedSYCNTaZcJFk12I5nXn5dzELmOMbT_6BqqojXJuyJ7nL5TWo</a>"},{"pid":"f63dbe0aeaced4ccaca938723e7ef65833aaf803","tid":2195030,"uid":21575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-0